        <num>CC 1917</num>
        <heading>1917.  Rules applicable to all kinds of obligations</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1917.  Rules applicable to all kinds of obligations
The rules of this title are applicable also to obligations that arise from sources other than contract to the extent that those rules are compatible with the nature of those obligations.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=109164</p>
